OL,3,CIsle of Wight Festival 2026: Who's
OL,4,Cperforming - and how can I get there?
OL,6,FIt marks his return to the festival,
OL,7,Ffollowing two years away in which he
OL,8,Fmade public his struggles with
OL,9,Fmanaging the symptoms of Tourette
OL,10,Fsyndrome
OL,12,FOther notable acts on Friday include
OL,13,FWet Legg and Two Door Cinema Club.
OL,15,FAmerican star Teddy Swims and Rita Ora
OL,16,Fwill entertain fans before DJ Calvin
OL,17,FHarris rounds off the evening's
OL,18,Fentertainment on Saturday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
