OL,3,CIsle of Wight Festival 2026: Who's
OL,4,Cperforming - and how can I get there?
OL,6,FThe festival will be closed out on
OL,7,FSunday with a show stopping
OL,8,Fperformance from The Cure, who are
OL,9,Fexpected to perform a number of crowd
OL,10,Ffavourites as well as tracks from
OL,11,Ftheir latest studio album, Songs Of A
OL,12,FLost World.
OL,14,FThis year's lineup has been described
OL,15,Fas possibly the festival's "best yet"
OL,16,Fby its director Caroline Giddings.
OL,18,FDon't drink and drive
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
