PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1781974080
OL,3,CIsle of Wight Festival 2026: Who's
OL,4,Cperforming - and how can I get there?
OL,6,FColin Evans, National Highways South
OL,7,FEast Region Road Safety Programme
OL,8,FManager, told ITV Meridian: "Have a
OL,9,Fgreat time, enjoy yourself, have a
OL,10,Fdrink by all means.
OL,12,F"But just think about that last day,
OL,13,Fthink about that morning after. It
OL,14,Fdoes take so much longer for it to go
OL,15,Fthrough your system than you might
OL,16,Fthink.
OL,18,F"A good breakfast might make you feel
OL,19,Fbetter, but it doesn't sober you up."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
